message.body: Hahah I don't really care about that. Oh no, I have a feeling that I will have a new obsession coming on, time to be a hermit and shirt everyone/everything out!
*shut
Heh. I think you'll be alright. You wanna watch season 1 with me?
Sure!
Awesome. Whenever you're available for a marathon just lemme know!
Sure, I will.
I had such a pleasant morning. Now I'm pissed off and annoyed!
Will ice cream make it better?
Yes, I've cream always makes everything better.
Let's get some. I could go for some green tea or something with chocolate
Today has been a fight to stay awake. It just feels like I haven't slept for days lol
So what was/is wrong?
It was stuff about my future work. I haven't even started and there's already an issue. I don't know if I could even start.
Probably not going to do ice cream tonight. Going to stay in to prep for tomorrow. I might be in the Center City area tomorrow. Can you do ice cream then?
Hope you downed the coffee.
Yeah. When is that gonna be?
Haha coffee doesn't affect me besides giving me a headache if I have enough of it. I drink it simply for the pleasant aroma
I'm not sure now.
Tea?
Red Bull?
Monster?
The day is over heh. It's ok.
5-hour Energy?
No, I don't touch any of the energy drinks.
Can I ask about why you can't start?
Can we talk?
Yeah, that's fine. Whenever you're ready.
I just had to do a background check form online. It took soooo long!
That's how it goes. Think you're making good strides tonight?
I guess. I feel better finishing that stuff online.
I'm glad. Guess I'll turn in then. Goodluck again :)
